  "title": "Common Man Coffee Roasters - Specialty Coffee Baristas Wanted !",
  "description": "<p><strong>Craft, Caffeine & Community: Elevate Your Barista Career with Common Man Coffee Roasters</strong></p><p>Are you passionate about the art of specialty coffee? Whether you're a seasoned barista looking to refine your craft or a junior barista with hands-on experience eager to grow, <strong>Common Man Coffee Roasters (CMCR)</strong> welcomes dedicated coffee lovers ready to take the next step in their journey.</p><p><strong>We’re Hiring For:</strong><br />📍 CMCR @ Martin Road<br />📍 CMCR @ Joo Chiat<br />📍 CMCR @ Quayside Isle (Sentosa)<br /></p><p><strong>Why CMCR?</strong></p><p><strong>🌱 Grow With the Best</strong><br />Work alongside some of the industry's most dedicated professionals. Whether you're refining your espresso dial-ins or elevating your latte art game, you’ll be mentored by our Head and Assistant Head Baristas who are committed to sharing their expertise.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🚀 Career Progression</strong><br />We don’t just hire baristas — we grow future coffee leaders. With clear promotion paths and opportunities across our group of brands, your career can evolve with us.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🤝 A Coffee-First Culture</strong><br />Join a crew that geeks out over grind size and extraction yield. We foster a supportive, quality-driven environment where craftsmanship, consistency, and curiosity are at the heart of everything we do.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>What You'll Be Great At (and Keep Getting Better At):</strong></p><ul><li>Espresso calibration and extraction</li><li>Precise milk texturing and pouring</li><li>Creative and consistent latte art</li><li>Deepening your coffee knowledge, from seed to cup</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Perks & Benefits:</strong><br />💰 <strong>Competitive Salary</strong><br />📅 <strong>5-Day Work Week</strong> (44-hour roster for true work-life balance)<br />🏥 <strong>Medical & Dental Coverage</strong><br />🍽️ <strong>Staff Meals & Discounts</strong> across all Spa Esprit Group outlets<br />🎁 <strong>Bonuses & Incentives</strong> — performance bonuses, sign-up and referral rewards!</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to brew with the best?</strong><br />Apply today and be part of a team where coffee craft, community, and career all come together!</p>",
